section.title: Gallery
section.intro: As an option, you can include some copy here to introduce your gallery. You can edit your gallery headings, what order they appear in, and the order of your images within each gallery.

section.title: News
section.intro: This is an example of a 'Multi page section'. You can have as many of these as you like on your web site. To remove this copy, go to 'Sections' in the admin system and click on edit against 'Multiple page section'.

section.title: Info
section.intro: This is an example of a single page section. It can display text and images.
section.copy: [image id="10700247" thumbnail="Yes" popup="yes"] You can use this optional section as a general information sheet. You can rename it whatever you like - or not have it at all if you so wish. Some use it as a price list for their services. Others as a general 'About me' page, with some more detailed information that could not be included on your home page. Clubs could use it as a noticeboard or general information page. It's entirely up to you.

section.title: Contact us
section.intro: Use this form to contact us. Please remember to check your email details are correct!
